icosteroids on theophylline metabolism." Ann Allergy 50 (1983): 249-51[4] Elvey SM, Saccar CL, Rocci ML, Mansmann HC, Martynec DM, Kester MB "The effect of corticosteroids on theophylline metabolim in asthmatic children." Ann Allergy 56 (1986): 520[5] Tatsis G, Orphanidou D, Douratsos D, et al "The effect of steroids on theophylline absorption." J Int Med Res 19 (1991): 326-9[6] Anderson JL, Ayres JW, Hall CA "Potential pharmacokinetic interaction between theophylline and prednisone." Clin Pharm 3 (1984): 187-8', 1767369485);
